These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, june, july
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, photography, dancing, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, rugby, sailing
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's hobby is photography##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in june##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | june   | july      | november   | may  |
| Hobby   | drawing    | dancing   | collecting | photography  |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton | rugby     | ice-hockey |

