.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, snowmobile, train, jet-ski
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, pall-mall, old-henry, aristoff
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking sprite is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
 4. the person drinking water is the person driving the train##1
 5. the person driving the subway is the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the person driving the train is the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
 9. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking sprite##7
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up         | sprite    | water  |
| Transport          | jet-ski     | snowmobile | subway | train |
| Cigar   | cain     | pall-mall     | old-henry  | aristoff |

