.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, romance, crime, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, gospel, classical, techno
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, bus, taxi
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
2. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
4. the fan of punk is between the fan of techno and the person watching crime movies##2
5. the person watching crime movies is not the person driving the taxi##6
6. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the fan of gospel##7
7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | crime  | romance  | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | classical | punk | techno     |
| Transport     | taxi    | bike     | boat     | bus         |

