.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, lizard, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, rugby, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, quad-bike, ship
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the owner of the snake is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is the owner of the cat##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is the person driving the airplane##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
8. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the owner of the lizard##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Pet   | snake    | hedgehog     | cat   | lizard      |
| Sport   | cricket    | badminton | rugby | baseball  |
| Transport     | motorbike | airplane  | ship    | quad-bike |

