 4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
 7. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsiris##7
 8. the art-deco house is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
